OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,Fare investigating what they have
OL,7,Fcalled a "truly horrific incident" at
OL,8,Fa funeral business in East Yorkshire.
OL,10,FOfficers began looking into Legacy
OL,11,FIndependent Funeral Directors, based
OL,12,Fin Hull, after receiving a call on 6
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FSince then, their enquiries have
OL,16,Fescalated, prompting a press
OL,17,Fconference on Tuesday, 12 March.
OL,19,FHere is everything we know about the
OL,20,Finvestigation so far.
