OL,6,FWho are Legacy Independent Funeral
OL,7,FDirectors?
OL,9,FAccording to its website, Legacy is a
OL,10,F"family business", led by funeral
OL,11,Fdirector and owner, Robert Bush.
OL,13,FEstablished in 2010, it expanded from
OL,14,Fits original branch on Anlaby Road in
OL,15,FHull to incorporate two further
OL,16,Fbranches ` a funeral home in Beverley
OL,17,Fand another on Hessle Road, Hull.
OL,19,F"Our structure allows us to provide a
OL,20,Fdedicated and unsurpassed personal
OL,21,Fservice," the website says.
