OL,6,F"As an independent funeral director,
OL,7,Fwe are able to create a unique
OL,8,Ffarewell for loved ones, with more
OL,9,Fflexibility and less constraint than
OL,10,Four competitors."
OL,12,FThe business is thought to have been a
OL,13,Fmember of the professional body, the
OL,14,FNational Association of Funeral
OL,15,FDirectors (NAFD), from 2011 but gave
OL,16,Fup its membership in 2021.
