OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, 6 March, a report was
OL,7,Fmade to police expressing concern
OL,8,Fabout the "storage and management
OL,9,Fprocesses relating to the care of the
OL,10,Fdeceased" at various locations run by
OL,11,FLegacy Funeral Directors.
OL,13,FPolice said that several enquiries
OL,14,Fwere made afterwards to "ascertain the
OL,15,Fexact details, concern and
OL,16,Fcircumstances".
OL,18,FA team of detectives started working
OL,19,Fwith partner agencies including Hull
OL,20,FCity Council, East Riding of Yorkshire
OL,21,FCouncil and His Majesty's Coroner.
