OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FOn Friday, 8 March, police said
OL,7,Fcordons were in place at all three
OL,8,Fsites.
OL,10,FA direct phone line was set up for
OL,11,Fanyone with concerns.
OL,13,FHull West and Hessle MP Emma Hardy
OL,14,Fsaid she was "extremely shocked" at
OL,15,Fthe investigation and could "only
OL,16,Fimagine the distress and devastation"
OL,17,Ffamilies felt.
