OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FA day later, on 9 March, Humberside
OL,7,FPolice confirmed it was in the process
OL,8,Fof moving "a number of deceased" from
OL,9,Fthe premises on Hessle Road to the
OL,10,Fcouncil's mortuary.
OL,12,FWhat are the allegations?
OL,14,FTwo people ` a 46-year-old man and a
OL,15,F23-year-old woman ` have been arrested
OL,16,Fon suspicion of prevention of a lawful
OL,17,Fand decent burial, fraud by false
OL,18,Frepresentation and fraud by abuse of
OL,19,Fposition.
OL,21,FThey have since been released on bail.
