OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FPolice have not been specific about
OL,7,Fthe nature of the alleged offences,
OL,8,Fbut have described what has happened
OL,9,Fas a "truly horrific incident".
OL,11,FDeputy Chief Constable David Marshall
OL,12,Ftold a press conference: "This is an
OL,13,Fextremely complex and sensitive
OL,14,Finvestigation, with heartbroken and
OL,15,Fdevastated families at the core of it."
OL,17,FAssistant Chief Constable Thom
OL,18,FMcLoughlin told families "we will do
OL,19,Feverything we possibly can to give you
OL,20,Fthe answers you deserve".
