OL,6,FHow many people are affected?
OL,8,FPolice said at Tuesday's press
OL,9,Fconference that they had moved 35
OL,10,Fbodies from the business's premises to
OL,11,Fthe city's mortuary.
OL,13,FThe force said a "quantity" of
OL,14,Fsuspected human ashes had also been
OL,15,Frecovered and were being
OL,16,F"respectfully" moved.
OL,18,FMore than 1,000 calls have been made
OL,19,Fto the dedicated phone line.
